Package proxy.flags

Class Flag

java.lang.Object
proxy.flags.Flag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Errors
Direct Known Subclasses:
CookiesFlag, FromListFlag, HTMLFlag, ImageFlag
public abstract class Flag extends Object implements Errors
An abstract class that represents a flag for a connection, such as "cookies" or "images".
